Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:23.24,Translator's Notes,,0,0,0,,T/N:  Power spots are places with great spiritual energy. Many Japanese people visit these places of spiritual significance to rejuvenate themselves in hopes of gaining greater powers. They usually are places that are important to Shinto/Buddhist religions or are historical spots.
